 {\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The crowds in Paris, however, have embraced both Khelif and Lin, who have heard nothing but cheers during their bouts.\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.787507077501181e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The crowds\", \"from\": 2771, \"to\": 2781}, {\"ngram\": \"both Khelif\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2834}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"their bouts\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A huge contingent of flag-waving Algeria fans greeted and serenaded Khelif throughout her semifinal victory Tuesday night, and she's become a hometown hero in her North African country.\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.99999545476099, \"rank\": 4.509497388775338e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9955896159816533, \"rank\": 0.00286832186967734, \"text\": \"North African\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A huge contingent\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2964}, {\"ngram\": \"her semifinal victory\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2997}, {\"ngram\": \"a hometown hero\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif has already secured Algeria's first Olympic medal in women's boxing.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3104, \"end\": 3111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.99999545476099, \"rank\": 4.509497388775338e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will attempt to become only her country's second boxing gold medalist, joining Hocine Soltani (1996).\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3236, \"end\": 3250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hocine Soltani\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hocine_Soltani\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only her country's second boxing gold medalist\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold medal fight is the culmination of Khelif's nine-day run through an Olympic tournament that began with a bizarre event.\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gold medal fight\", \"from\": 3260, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"the culmination\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's nine-day run\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3324}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic tournament\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3354}, {\"ngram\": \"a bizarre event\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif's first opponent, Angela Carini of Italy, abandoned their bout after just 46 seconds, saying she was in too much pain from Khelif's punches.\", \"from\": 3388, \"to\": 353